attributionInfo.agentName: Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection
Witter & Witter Boston / Cape Cod Connection

description: The perfect single-family does exist! This beautifully renovated home in South Boston’s sought-after East Side offers 3 bedrooms + a study/nursery, 2.5 baths, and the rare combination of deeded parking and a yard. The main level boasts a tasteful kitchen with stainless steel appliances, quartz counters, and ample storage, flowing seamlessly into a spacious dining and living area with a gas fireplace and built-ins, plus a 1/2 bath. A wall of windows opens to a large deck and fenced-in yard, ideal for entertaining and kids. Upstairs, you'll find two generous bedrooms, including a king-sized primary, an add'l study/nursery, and a stylish full bath with double vanities. The lower level features a 3rd bedroom, full bath, laundry, and an office/work out area. Full renovation in 2019 included upgrades such as exterior siding, windows, flooring, HVAC, and kitchen and baths. One direct-access parking space included. Prime East Side location, just moments from the beach, dining, and shopping.
